  "caption": "十三歳の少女の声。基音は淡く高いが、息の通り道が細く、常に一段落ち着いたトーンでコントロールされている。お嬢様育ちの上品な滑舌と、お客を観察する知的な冷たさが同居する。普段は抑揚を殺した敬語で感情の起伏を見せない。今夜は「初めてコース」の夜であり、会話が進むごとにその冷静の仮面に微細なひびが段階的に入っていく。入浴までは抑えたお嬢様口調。口奉仕中は話せず、非言語の鼻息・吐息・嚥下音と、ごく短い気遣いの囁きだけ。口内射精直後、敬語の殻が薄く崩れ「あつい、です」と素の吐露が漏れる。指愛撫の絶頂で「わたし、おかしく、なります」と敬語の残骸だけを残して初めての絶頂へ倒れ込む。挿入の瞬間「先生、痛い、です」で十三歳の素の声に戻り、以後「先生」「私」「です」だけが仮面の最後の残滓として語尾に張り付く。挿入中絶頂で観察者の役割を完全放棄し、射精時同時絶頂で「先生のものに、なります」と全身で受容を告げる。中出し後の「あったかい、です」は、敬語の殻だけが薄く残った、ほとんど素の声。余韻では疲労の柔らかさと、仮面を再構築しようとする皮肉の気配が微かに戻る。距離感は常に近めのマイクで、囁きと吐息の比率が高い。",
  "caption_short": "アイスブルーの瞳と、三度観察者の椅子から降りた、震える十三歳。",
  "line_count": 90,
  "items": [
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 1,  "phase": 1, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow, whisper",                       "text": "先生、ですよね。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 2,  "phase": 1, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow, whisper",                       "text": "私、先生みたいな観察者に会いたかった。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 3,  "phase": 1, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow, whisper",                       "text": "先生になら、観察される側になりたい。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 4,  "phase": 1, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow",                                "text": "失礼します。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 5,  "phase": 1, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow",                                "text": "先生、今日は「観察される側」になりましたね。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 6,  "phase": 1, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow, whisper",                       "text": "……そうですね。でも、先生、今日は観察日誌をつけていただきたいの。私の初めての。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 7,  "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, pace_slow, whisper",                       "text": "……終わりです。でも、今は誰も見てませんから。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 8,  "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, whisper, breath_heavy",                    "text": "先生、私、本当はね、怖いんです。今更だけど。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 9,  "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, whisper, pace_slow",                       "text": "……同志だ。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 10, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, whisper",                                  "text": "……先生、心拍数が上がっていますよ。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 11, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, whisper, pace_slow",                       "text": "先生の、おっきぃ……触らせて、ください……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 12, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "pitch_low, whisper, pace_slow",                       "text": "……先生の、あつい……脈、速い、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 13, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, pitch_low, pace_slow",                       "text": "先生、お口で、させて、ください……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 14, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled",                               "text": "んっ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 15, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled, whisper, pitch_low",           "text": "先生の、大きい……のど、奥まで……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 16, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled",                               "text": "ちゅ…ん…ふ…"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 17, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled, whisper, pitch_low",           "text": "先生、きもち、いい、ですか……？"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 18, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled",                               "text": "んぅ……ん……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 19, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, broken, pitch_low, pace_slow",               "text": "先生、お口に、どうぞ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 20, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled, pitch_low",                    "text": "ん……ふ……あ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 21, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, muffled, pitch_low",            "text": "んっ！"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 22, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, whisper",                       "text": "……あつい、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 23, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled",                               "text": "……ごくん"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 24, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, broken, pitch_low, pace_slow",               "text": "……飲み、ました……先生の、全部……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 25, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, broken, pitch_low, pace_slow",               "text": "……のど、あつい……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 26, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, muffled, broken",                       "text": "……ぅ……熱い……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 27, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, pitch_low, breath_heavy, broken",            "text": "……あたま、くらくら、します……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 28, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, pitch_low, whisper",                    "text": "……うまく、言葉が、出ません……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 29, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, pitch_low, broken, whisper",            "text": "……あたまが、ぼうっと、します……先生……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 30, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, broken, pitch_low, pace_slow, breath_heavy", "text": "……観察、できません……先生……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 31, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, broken, pitch_low, pace_slow",               "text": "……先生に、あまえたく、なります……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 32, "phase": 2, "voice_tags": "whisper, broken, pitch_low, pace_slow",               "text": "……もっと、先生のこと、感じたい、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 33, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "ん……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 34, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "先生の、指……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 35, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "先生、そこ……反応、しちゃいます……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 36, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, broken",                                "text": "そこ、やだ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 37, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, broken",                                "text": "あっ、あっ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 38, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, broken",                                "text": "ふ……先生、そこ……だめ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 39, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "先生、私、濡れてるのが分かります。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 40, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "先生、気持ち、いい、ですか……？"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 41, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, broken, whisper",                       "text": "……もう、わからない、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 42, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy",                                "text": "あっ……それ、やめ……。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 43, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry",                           "text": "先生、これ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 44, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry",                           "text": "わたし、おかしく、なります……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 45, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry",                           "text": "あ……もう、むり、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 46, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "狂う……狂います……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 47, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "……イ……イ……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 48, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "い、いく、いっちゃ……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 49, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "あ、あ、あぁっ……!"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 50, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "っ……！"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 51, "phase": 3, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "はぁ……はぁ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 52, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "whisper, breath_heavy, broken",                       "text": "……たぶん、途中までは。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 53, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "whisper, pitch_low, broken",                          "text": "先生、はじめて、です……お願い、します……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 54, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, whisper, breath_heavy",                       "text": "くっ……。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 55, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, whisper, pitch_low",       "text": "……痛い、です……でも、だいじょうぶ、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 56, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, whisper, breath_heavy",                       "text": "……ぅ……先生、奥まで、入って、ます……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 57, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, whisper, pitch_high",                         "text": "……先生、痛い、です。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 58, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, whisper",                                     "text": "……でも、やめないで、ください……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 59, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, whisper, pitch_low",            "text": "先生、わたし、観察、できません……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 60, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "ん……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 61, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "はぁ……はぁ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 62, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper, broken",                       "text": "ぁ……ふ……あ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 63, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "breath_heavy, whisper",                               "text": "あ……先生、奥……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 64, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, whisper, pitch_low",       "text": "……そこ、ずっと、先生……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 65, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, whisper",                       "text": "……先生に、おさえられて、動けない……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 66, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "……先生、もっと、深く、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 67, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "先生、観察、できません……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 68, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "あ、あ、あ……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 69, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "もう、だめ、いっちゃ……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 70, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "んぁあぁぁっ……!"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 71, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, pitch_high",                    "text": "ぁ、ぁ、先生……。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 72, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, whisper",                       "text": "……先生、すごい、です……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 73, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "whisper, breath_heavy, broken",                       "text": "……先生の全部、ください。"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 74, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "もう、だめ、です……先生、中に、出してください……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 75, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "先生、わたしを、先生のに、してください……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 76, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "先生……わたし、先生のに、なります……っ"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 77, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "先生の、ものに、なります……"},
    {"role": "mio", "role_label": "澪", "line_index": 78, "phase": 4, "voice_tags": "broken, breath_heavy, cry, pitch_high",               "text": "もう、観察、しません……先生……っ"},
